Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要我打聽情報我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且諾拉又不值得信任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等艾露希回來就轉告她讓她來見我一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…是嘉音？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.69,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look up at the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:32.32,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Like a bird without wings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:34.72,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}If you want to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:38.08,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Feel your breeze, release yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.60,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:42.19,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:44.55,op,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Every time you try
